                     <interp inst="t17610916-49-person466" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner made me a present of two pair of stockings. [Producing them, and deposed to by the prosecutor.]</p>
               <p>Q. When did he give them to you?</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17610916-49-person467">
                  Howell 
                  It 
               <interp inst="t17610916-49-person467" type="surname" value="It"></interp>
